            Nucleotidyltransferases
SYSNAME     CTP:N,N'-diacetyllegionaminate cytidylyltransferase
REACTION    CTP + N,N'-diacetyllegionaminate = CMP-N,N'-diacetyllegionaminate + diphosphate [RN:R10182]
